# Redirect HTTP to HTTPS
http://berez.in/* https://www.berez.in/:splat 301!
http://www.berez.in/* https://www.berez.in/:splat 301!

# Redirect non-www to www
https://berez.in/* https://www.berez.in/:splat 301!

# Redirect old WordPress paths to homepage (optional - you can remove this if you prefer 404s)
/wp-content/* / 301
